						<p>Impression is not available for this record. It registers a gift of 45 sheep by Dānamakramavittaṇ, a (resident) of Kāṭṭur in order to burn half a lamp to deity of Tiruvālīśvaram at Kāṭṭūr in Paiyyūr-kōṭṭam.</p>						

